Insider Activity


Individual




Steven B. Hedlund



Mr. Steven B. Hedlund is EVP & President-International Welding segment at Lincoln Electric Holdings, Inc. and Senior VP & President-Global Automation at The Lincoln Electric Co. Mr. Hedlund was previously employed as VP-Strategic Planning & New Business Development by Beam Suntory, Inc., a Principal by Booz Allen Hamilton, Inc., and Vice President-Growth & Innovation by Master Lock Co. LLC. He received his undergraduate degree from Dartmouth College and an MBA from Dartmouth College.



